snippet.title: CENTRAL STATION: A TURN BASED RPG (2015)
snippet.description:
A free turn based RPG, set in a surreal world. 
Download: http://www.mediafire.com/file/d3ky3zhgd6faji7/MODERN+-+Central+Station+-+stable+2015.rar
Features:

    -you can save your game
    -fight hand painted enemies
    -engage in turn based combat
    -explore a new world
    -solve puzzles
    -immerse yourself in the lore


//known issues//

2nd secret area cannot be unlocked
miser party member has a broken move that targets allies instead of enemies

i don't have the original files for this anymore, I can't fix it
